column1: # Readings for January-March, May, July and September-December 1936 are estimates and have been omitted.
# The reading for January 1937 is an estimate and has been omitted.
# The readings for January and February 1940 are part-estimates for snow and have been retained.
# The reading for January 1941 is a apportioned (with what?) for snow.
# The reading for February 1947 is an estimate and has been omitted.
# The readings for January and February 1950 are apportioned.
# The station continued until 2016 according to MIDAS.
